\fs48 General
\fs28 \
\
Automatically start VIstaClock at Login
\f0\b0  \'96 Starts the program automatically when you log in to the computer.\
\

\f1\b Automatically hide VistaClock
\f0\b0  \'96 Automatically hides the panel when it loses focus.\
\

\f1\b Keep on Top
\f0\b0  \'96 Forces the panel to stay on top of all other windows.\
\

\f1\b Use shadows 
\f0\b0 \'96 Show panel fonts with a shadow.\
\

\f1\b Use Large Fonts
\f0\b0  \'96 Use large fonts on the panel.\
\

\f1\b Show Dock Clock
\f0\b0  \'96 Show the first configured clock in the dock.  (This option will significantly increase CPU usage and energy consumption. This option will also prohibit VistaClock to be shown on top of full screen applications.)\
\
\

