\fs28 \
\
Enable Date Time Options
\f0\b0  \'96 Show date and time options to allow date time on the menu bar else, show just an icon.\
\

\f1\b Use Black & White Icon
\f0\b0  \'96 If showing just an icon instead of the date time, then show it as black and white.\
\

\f1\b Show Week Number Icon
\f0\b0  \'96 Show the current week number on the menu bar.\
\

\f1\b Use Black & White Week Number Icon
