\

\f1\b Use Fuzzy Time
\f0\b0  \'96 Use fuzzy time for text on the menu bar.\
\

\f1\b Use Inverse Color
\f0\b0  \'96 Use inverse color for text on the menu bar.
\f1\b \
\
Show Date
